<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Developer Portfolio</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>

  <style>
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    section {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body data-bs-spy="scroll" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" data-bs-offset="70">
  <nav id="navbar" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top">
    <a class="navbar-brand p-2">Candace Fisher</a>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
      <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#bio">Bio</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#projects">Projects</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Resume
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section id="bio" class="bg-light text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>I am aÂ Software Developer with years of experience in designing, developing, and maintaining a high-performance web application. My expertise includes Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, RESTful APIs, and Python. My experience spans code migration, UI enhancements, automation, production support, and performance optimization. I am also skilled in database management, third-party API integrations, and building scalable, secure solutions. Beyond development, I actively engage in code reviews, agile methodologies, and cross-functional collaboration to drive business value. I have a solid understanding of Microsoft Power BI to enhance productivity and analyze data. I am passionate about continuous learning, problem-solving, and crafting software solutions that enhance user experience and operational efficiency. Let's connect to explore how I can contribute to your next project!</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="projects" class="text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/CeeFish/my_portfolio" target="_blank">My Portfolio</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/CodeTheDream/upstate" target="_blank">UpState</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contact Me</h2>
      <% if flash[:notice] %>
      <div class="alert alert-success"><%= flash[:notice] %></div>
      <% end %>

      <%= form_with url: contact_path, method: :post, local: true, class: "text-start mx-auto" do |f| %>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <%= f.label :name %>
        <%= f.text_field :name, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <%= f.label :email %>
        <%= f.email_field :email, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <%= f.label :phone %>
        <%= f.telephone_field :phone, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <%= f.label :message %>
        <%= f.text_area :message, rows: 4, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>
      <%= f.submit "Send Message", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3">
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3">
      <a href="https://github.com/CeeFish" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="GitHub (opens in new tab)" class="text-white fs-4">
        <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/candace-fisher-mba-developer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn (opens in new tab)" class="text-white fs-4">
        <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="mailto:youremail@example.com" aria-label="Send email" class="text-white fs-4">
        <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-2 small">
      &copy; <%= Date.today.year %> Candace Fisher
    </div>
  </footer>


</body>

</html>
